{
  "stem": "8072.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had some clothes they were selling, to do something to make-- to survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my brother and another couple from-- that lived there already, they were liberated earlier, they were going to our hometown.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, I'll go with you guys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went with them to [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Volbroch. ?] We got there around sunset-- I don't know what time-- and we were going to stay at this one farm overnight.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the barn, not in a hotel, in the barn, staying there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he, around 10 o'clock at night, he comes in and he says, my daughter overheard something that somebody saw us arrive in town.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he-- they might-- somebody might want to hurt us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he doesn't want us to get hurt in town, and everything like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That he rather we would leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was dark-- pitch-- you know, you don't have lighting like you have in here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In a, in a farm in Poland--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, from then--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we wanted to go back to Sosnowiec, and we stopped about halfway down the road.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a train, a train, in their station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got there, and there was this Polish lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing you're good is to take you to the woods and to kill you like dogs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I really thought he was going to do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they all had money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he took their money away, and he let them go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And me, he was-- he wrote up a big report.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was going to keep me because I didn't honor the Polish government.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
